	[em 
		"Thomas the Tank Engine & Friends
	]em
	" is a licensed video game for the Sega Genesis that's based on the British animated series of the same name. Created for the franchise's very young audience, the game features a coloring book mode where you get to color in line art of various 
	[em 
		"Thomas & Friends
	]em
	" characters and three modes where you control Thomas himself. They include a "Game" mode where the objective is to deliver freight cars to various stations, a "Race" mode where you race against another train engine, and an "Explore" mode that allows you to freely roam around the map.
